        "content": "<p>I see <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/GeneralLinearGroup/Card.html#Matrix.card_GL_field\">https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/GeneralLinearGroup/Card.html#Matrix.card_GL_field</a></p>\n<p>but can't seem to find the corresponding theorem for the SpecialLinearGroup. </p>\n<p>Also, there are so many different cardinality functions <code>Fintype.card</code>, <code>Nat.card</code>, and others, which one is the canonical one to use for such theorems.</p>",
